org.dacapo.harness

Class CommandLineArgs

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dacapo.harness.CommandLineArgs

  • public class CommandLineArgs
extends java.lang.Object
    Command line arguments for a dacapo benchmark run. Encapsulated in an object so that it can be passed to user-written callbacks.
